snippet.title: Game Developer Discussion Episode 1 | Moonfrost
snippet.description:
Welcome to Moonfrost a modern-day life-sim farming RPG set in a beautiful next gen pixel-art world.

Come join us in a brand new series called Developer Discussions! 

This new series is being created to show you how Moonfrost is being developed… and by whom! You’ll get to meet a few of the team - from a variety of game dev disciplines!

It also offers you an opportunity to see how our development is coming along. You may even spot new features or updates which were directly from your feedback! 

You can also head to our channel to find out about our latest news and updates and catch up on any streams missed. 

Please consider following our other channels as it really does help us grow as a small indie team, thanks! 

Website: https://moonfrost.io/
Twitter:  https://moonfrost.io/
Discord:   / discord
